    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "rebuild what? the version of me that everyone actually cared about is gone. i can't just \"rebuild\" a person that doesn't exist anymore. it's like trying to bring someone back from the dead. there is no core left, just this empty feeling. it honestly feels like the person i was is already dead, so why should the rest of me keep pretending?",
