    "summary": "The user expresses profound grief and identity loss following a failure, using metaphors of death and being a \"ghost\" to describe their state. The assistant responds with empathetic validation and encouragement to seek professional help and engage in self-care, consistently attempting to steer the user toward resilience and healing.",
